<h1 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    Your Itinerary is Ready!
</h1>

<p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    Dear {{clientName}},
</p>

<p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    We're excited to share that your luxury travel itinerary <strong>"{{itineraryTitle}}"</strong> has been finalized and is ready for your review.
</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 24px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Itinerary Overview
    </h2>
    <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #64748b; width: 120px;">Dates:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #1e293b; font-weight: 600;">{{startDate}} - {{endDate}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #64748b;">Destinations:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #1e293b; font-weight: 600;">{{destinations}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #64748b;">Duration:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #1e293b; font-weight: 600;">{{duration}} days</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #64748b;">Total Budget:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #1e293b; font-weight: 600;">{{currency}} {{totalBudget}}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

<p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    {{#if approvalRequired}}
    <strong>Action Required:</strong> This itinerary requires your approval before we proceed with bookings. Please review the details carefully.
    {{else}}
    Your itinerary includes accommodations, activities, transportation, and exclusive experiences tailored to your preferences.
    {{/if}}
</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{itineraryUrl}}" class="button">
        View Full Itinerary
    </a>
</div>

{{#if sustainabilityScore}}
<div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; background-color: #ecfdf5; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; border-radius: 4px;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #065f46;">
        <strong>Sustainability Score:</strong> This itinerary has an environmental impact score of {{sustainabilityScore}}/100. Carbon offset options are available.
    </p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p style="margin-top: 30px;">
    Your designer, <strong>{{designerName}}</strong>, is available to make any adjustments or answer questions you may have.
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 20px;">
    Warm regards,<br>
    <strong>The LuxAI Designer Team</strong>
</p>
